'''Islam''' d [[ajjed]] ideg ttamnen medden belli [[Yakuc]] (Rebbi), ur yesɛi mmi-s ur yesɛi tameṭṭut. Ɣur-s lemluk i t-ttɛawanen, yuzen rrusel ɣur medden akken ad ttamnen yis-es. Rrasul aneggaru deg lislam d [[Muḥemmed]].

Isem n medden i yettamnen s lislam, inselmen. Inselmen ɣur-sen 5 n tamara:

*Lḥeǧǧ.
*taẓallit.
*Cchada.
*Remḍan.
*Zzakat.

Deg lislam, yella yiwen wedlis : [[leqran]], yella daɣen [[lḥadit]] neɣ timucuha ɣef tudert n [[Muḥemmed]]. Inselmen ttamnen belli [[inǧil]] d [[turat]] ttubeddlen, mačči am yuzen-aten Rebbi.

